om_to_window_filter_narrows_the_result, test_export_with_no_filters_returns_all_caller_rows\", \"reason\": \"each filter independently narrows the row set; all-omitted returns full set\" },\n      { \"id\": \"AC3\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/test_schemas_usage_export.py::test_from_alias_binds_to_from__field, test_rejects_naive_from_datetime, test_rejects_naive_to_datetime, test_rejects_from_after_to, test_accepts_from_equal_to_to, test_rejects_from_too_far_in_the_past, test_rejects_to_too_far_in_the_future\", \"reason\": \"naive-reject, inverted-range-reject, and both window-bound edges (90d/1h) exercised\" },\n      { \"id\": \"AC4\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/test_schemas_usage_export.py::test_rejects_injection_in_customer_id, test_rejects_unknown_fields; tests/integration/test_usage_export_endpoint.py::test_export_malformed_query_param_returns_422, test_export_unknown_query_param_returns_422\", \"reason\": \"422 envelope + extra=forbid verified at unit and integration tiers\" },\n      { \"id\": \"AC5\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/integration/test_usage_export_endpoint.py::test_export_rate_limit_two_principals_one_ip_get_independent_buckets\", \"reason\": \"discriminating two-principals-one-IP shape (not the weak same-owner-only form) proves the Tier-2 throttle is keyed on api_key_id, not client IP\" },\n      { \"id\": \"AC6\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/integration/test_usage_export_endpoint.py::test_export_requires_authentication, test_export_any_authenticated_scope_may_export_ingest_and_admin\", \"reason\": \"no/invalid key -> 401; both ingest- and admin-scoped keys -> 200 (no scope gate)\" },\n      { \"id\": \"AC7\", \"covered\": true, \"test\": \"tests/integration/test_usage_export_endpoint.py::test_export_tenant_isolation_excludes_other_tenants_rows\", \"reason\": \"IDOR/BOLA shape: two tenants share a customer_id value; tenant A's export excludes tenant B's row by value, not just by count\" },\n      { \"id\": \"